tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE MapNavigation (
  map_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  map_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  map_data JSON NOT NULL,
  last_update TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE maps (
 id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 map_name STRING,
 map_data JSONB
)

CREATE TABLE vehicles (
 id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 vehicle_name STRING,
 model STRING,
 manufacturer STRING,
 year INTEGER
)

CREATE TABLE routes (
 id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 route_name STRING,
 start_point STRING,
 end_point STRING,
 distance_km FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE updates (
 id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 update_time TIMESTAMP,
 update_type STRING,
 description TEXT
)
